         <div type="translation">
            <ab>To Aurelius Iulius Isidoros, strategos of the Arsinoite nome, Herakleides division, from Aurelius Pasion, village secretary of Philadelphia. For the delivery of prisoners being sent to Alexandria to the most illustrious prefect Aurelius Septimius Heraclitus [I submit the] persons written below, since they are [men of property and] qualified [- - -]</ab>
